readme: # parrot-dark-syntax A pretty syntax theme in Atom editor. Recommend use it with dark UI theme. Similar to [Johny Georges's JetJet-theme in VScode](https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=JohnyGeorges.jetjet-theme). ## usage there are 2 recommend ways to install: - enter apm install parrot-dark-syntax in your command line. - In editor setting page, select install at left panel, input parrot-dark-syntax and search in Theme type, then install it. Enjoy it !
